snippet.title: Nested Lands Feature Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to Nested Lands, a ruthless medieval survival settlement RPG set in a dark, plague-ravaged world where twisted madmen and bandits roam the land. Find and recruit survivors, build a settlement, craft, master your skills and endure alone or in online co-op.

Wishlist Nested Lands here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2553040/Nested_Lands/

Nested Lands Discord: https://discord.gg/GQ2WAjmxj2

#nestedlands #survivalgames #managementgames #darkgames
